 watch lists ‚Äì</strong> keep a track of multi markets and multi trading opportunities so you are right up to date at a glance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="565" img_size="full" alignment="right" css=".vc_custom_1489925910771{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482231549953{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]<strong>Benefit from online trading ‚Äì</strong> trades go straight to the individual exchanges, not through brokerage houses ‚Äì saving you time and money.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="559" img_size="full" alignment="right" css=".vc_custom_1489925833147{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482231577526{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]<strong>Benefit from a wide range of analysis,</strong> chart, a ‚ÄòWhat if‚Äô calculator, cash flow analysis, volume watch, strategy monitor and performance map. Work out best times to buy and sell using our feature rich, easy to use charting tools.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="561" img_size="full" alignment="right" css=".vc_custom_1489925892262{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1489928599112{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]<strong>See detailed</strong> <strong>company quotes</strong>, showing graphs, prices, volume and turnover. See unrivalled market depth by price.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="566" img_size="full" alignment="right" css=".vc_custom_1489925900778{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482378020859{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]<strong>See top stocks &amp; market indices</strong> for all markets covered. Mubasher Pro provides you with a rich set of data to help you make investment decisions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="560" img_size="full" alignment="right" css=".vc_custom_1489925881832{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482231585770{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]<strong>Rest assured ‚Äì</strong> Mubasher Pro is operated by Mubasher Financial Services (MFS) one of the leading brokerage houses based in the Middle East. MFS is incorporated in Bahrain and holds licence category two.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:17:"MubasherTrade Pro";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"mubashertrade-pro";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0: