<div class="mrkt-acco-wrpp"><span class="market_general_title">Priority</span></div>
<ul>
 	<li>Price - the order with the best price has the highest queue priority</li>
 	<li>Cross - the lowest priority is given for matching an order of the same buyer and seller broker</li>
