 	<li>Special Term - orders with the least trading restrictions will be given priority over orders with greater restrictions</li>
 	<li>Amend order price or quantity will loss the priority if increase the price, Increase the Quantity, or decrease the price , the only case will not loss the priority if decrease the quantity</li>
</ul>
